Sunken chest
Type: Container

From the depths of the sea, this chest has found its way to the shore.

Sunken chest is an openable treasury item. It can be dropped from some sea related activities. They can have the odds of finding them increased with the Chest Finding equipment attribute.

Loot Tables

These are the sub-tables for the various materials, coins, and items that can come from these chests.

These treasury items take 4 independent loot rolls when they are opened.
